  Elastic & Less than infinity but greater than 1 & The percentage increase in the quantity supplied exceeds the percentage increase in the price \\
  Inelastic & Greater than zero but less than 1 & The percentage increase in the quantity supplied is less than the percentage increase in the price \\
  Perfectly inelastic & Zero & The quantity supplied is the same at all prices \\
